Tomorrow .. A publication calling for & quot; drunken ways of corruption & quot;
05 Nov 2019, 17:50 by Lebanon 24
Trading will take place on social media with a brochure entitled "Drunken Corruption Roads" starting tomorrow at 9:00 am. The circular called on citizens to come down to the nearest institution and demonstrate in front of it and close it.
